<h3 class="sectionHeader">A Year at War</h3>

  <p><em>In Command</em></p>
<p class="summary">Articles in this series are chronicling the yearlong deployment of the First Battalion, 87th Infantry Regiment, based in Kunduz Province, Afghanistan. The series follows the battalion’s part in the surge in northern Afghanistan and the impact of war on individual soldiers and their families back home.</p>
  
